件工作<br />\n咁啲真正重要嘅軟件工作就會被一拖再拖，掉埋一邊<br />\n咁好可能<br />\n個 IOS 就可能無咁多真正好嘅功能<br />\n同時又會有好多 Bugs"},{"pid":"133d230de8fb438157757043759e8f8e47170d87","tid":562080,"uid":73095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"前蘋果工程師爆料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係要簽保密協議咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d676d0ebba0509f8f2bbd297cb50303c57b54a8","tid":562080,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb5165924016b8cdfb963c398a5bd429d565c88","tid":562080,"uid":23682,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4cb9017e97602e01170cddf47f06732f30502f2a","tid":562080,"uid":15835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"係咪得我睇唔明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"睇咗3次都唔明點解ios11多bug<br />\n淨係見到話d manager亂排project嘅優先次序<br />\n令到d細嘅做到狗咁<br />\n咁點解多bug？<br />\n係咪想講大壓力所以做錯？定時間太短唔夠debug？咁debug未完成點解又要出街？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"可能係佢想講啲P3P4因為非緊急所以唔理住，點知啲bugs係由P3P4度走出嚟"},{"pid":"8e405526a52f58fa30ad3ec3a921e89833e01c98","tid":562080,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c640365d7fb1d189ad8e88cec4dbde4e88546f5","tid":562080,"uid":60179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"133d230de8fb438157757043759e8f8e47170d87","tid":562080,"uid":73095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"前蘋果工程師爆料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係要簽保密協議咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"唔洗講到咁白啦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75ee527ed914016b17a8ecb5cced71132fd4f75","tid":562080,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,